SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION USES AN OUTSIDE SERVICE CALLED COTTINGHAM AND BUTLER TO DO AN INDEPENDENT WAGE AND COMPENSATION ASSESSMENT. A REVIEW IS COMPLETED EVERY 3 YEARS OF ALL JOB DESCRIPTIONS WITH ANNUAL REVIEWS OF SPECIFIC JOBS IN THE INTERIM YEARS. THIS ANALYSIS IS THEN SHARED WITH THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS TO UTILIZE IN REVIEWING AND SETTING WAGES FOR EVERYONE WITHIN THE ORGANIZATION, INCLUDING OFFICERS, DIRECTORS, KEY EMPLOYEES, ETC. THE REVIEW OF THIS INFORMATION WOULD BE DOCUMENTED IN THE MEETING MINUTES OF THE MANAGEMENT ENTITY'S BOARD OF DRIECTORS. THE MOST RECENT FULL REVIEW WAS IN 2018 AND THE NEXT FULL REVIEW WILL BE COMPLETED IN 2021.
